---
// LanguageSwitcher.astro - Language switcher component
---

<div id="lang-switcher" class="row-span-2 col-start-4 bg-gradient-to-br bg-[#5B3E96] rounded-3xl p-4 text-white flex flex-col justify-center items-center select-none">
  <div id="lang-current" class="text-6xl font-extrabold text-white mb-2 transition-all duration-200">EN</div>
  <div class="flex gap-2 text-base font-bold">
    <span id="lang-en-label" class="transition-all duration-200">EN</span>
    <span id="lang-es-label" class="transition-all duration-200">ES</span>
  </div>
</div> 